    "description": "<p>CHAPTR is a specialist recruitment firm that focuses on offering advice about career transformation, strategic employer branding, and talent consulting. <br>\n<br>\nWe offer a high level of expertise in Singapore's employment landscape and are deeply connected with some of the world's greatest companies, including the most aspiring start-ups and a large pool of talented individuals across industries. <br>\n<br>\nOur mission is to support job seekers and companies alike. We take pride in finding the best candidates for our clients while also helping our associates achieve their professional goals. <br>\n<br>\nOur commitment to our clients is unwavering and extends beyond the hiring process, as we strive to become long-term advisors, providing guidance and support to individuals as they navigate their career paths.<br>\n<br>\nWith us, your next chapter begins.</p>",
